'''[[小型计算机系统接口|SCSI]]週邊裝置'''透過用以描述裝置'''SCSI週邊裝置類型'''的查詢功能，以傳回數值第一個字節中的五位字段來表示裝置的類型<ref name="SPC-4">{{cite book |url=http://www.t10.org/cgi-bin/ac.pl?t=f&f=spc4r36d.pdf ° |format=PDF |title=Draft of SCSI Primary Commands - 4 (SPC-4 r36d) |chapter=section 6.6.2 - Standard INQUIRY data |language=en |access-date=2022-04-25 |archive-date=2021-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211109191622/https://www.t10.org/cgi-bin/ac.pl?t=f&f=spc4r36d.pdf }}</ref>。

底下這些描述是在SCSI命令裡面Inquiry命令的Inquiry data的SCSI Peripheral Device Type這個欄位的定義。

{| class="wikitable sortable"
|+
|-
! 數值 !! 裝置類型 ||Command set ||Specification
|-
|00h || 直接存取區塊裝置（例如：磁碟機） ||SBC Direct Access Commands ||''SCSI Block Commands'' (SBC)
|-
|01h || 循序存取裝置（例如：磁帶機） ||SSC Sequential Access Commands ||''SCSI Stream Commands'' (SSC)
|-
|02h || 列印裝置 ||SSC Printer Commands ||''SCSI Stream Commands'' (SSC)
|-
|03h || 處理器裝置 ||SPC Processor Commands ||''SCSI Primary Commands'' (SPC)
|-
|04h || 一次寫入裝置 ||SBC Write Once Commands ||''SCSI Block Commands'' (SBC)
|-
|05h || [[雷射唱片|CD]]/[[DVD|DVD]]-ROM驱动 ||MMC CD-ROM Commands ||''{{tsl|en|MultiMedia Commands||SCSI Multimedia Commands}}'' (MMC)
|-
|06h || 掃描裝置 ||SGC Scanner Commands ||''SCSI Graphics Commands'' (SGC)
|-
|08h ||中型装载装置（例如：[[光碟櫃|光碟櫃]]） ||SMC Medium Changer Commands ||''SCSI Medium Changer Commands'' (SMC)
|-
|07h || 光學記憶裝置 （例如：[[光盘|光盘]]） ||SBC Optical Media Commands ||''SCSI Block Commands'' (SBC)
|-
|09h || 通訊裝置 ||SSC Communications Commands ||''SCSI Stream Commands'' (SSC)
|-
|0Ah–0Bh ||Defined by ASC IT8 (Graphic arts pre-press devices) ||ASC IT8 Prepress Commands
|-
|0Ch ||存储矩阵控制器（例如：[[RAID|RAID]]） ||SCC Array Controller Commands ||''SCSI Controller Commands'' (SCC)
|-
|0Dh || [[機殼管理裝置|機殼管理裝置]] ||SES Enclosure Services Commands ||''[[SCSI箱體服務|SCSI Enclosure Services]]'' (SES)
|-
|0Eh ||简易直接访问驱动器（例如：[[磁儲存|磁儲存]]） ||RBC Reduced Block Commands ||''Reduced Block Commands'' (RBC)
|-
|0Fh ||智能卡读写器 ||OCRW Optical Card Commands ||''SCSI Specification for Optical Card Reader/Writer'' (OCRW)
|-
|10h ||保留用于桥接扩展器
|-
|11h ||基于对象存储驱动器 ||OSD Object-based Storage Commands ||''Object-based Storage Commands'' (OSD)
|-
|12h ||Automation/Drive Interface
|-
|13h ||安全管理设备
|-
|14h || Host managed zoned block device<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.t10.org/cgi-bin/ac.pl?t=f&f=spc5r10.pdf |title=Draft of SCSI Primary Commands - 5 (SPC-5 r10), section 6.6.2 - Standard INQUIRY data |access-date=2022-04-25 |archive-date=2021-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211109191647/https://www.t10.org/cgi-bin/ac.pl?t=f&f=spc5r10.pdf }}</ref> || ||''Zoned Block Commands'' (ZBC)
|-
|15h || ||RMC Simplified Multimedia Commands ||''Reduced Multimedia Commands'' (RMC)
|-
|16h–1Dh || 保留
|-
|1Eh ||Well known logical unit
|-
|1Fh || 未知，或沒設置裝置類型
|}

